---
import Hero from "@/components/blocks/Hero.astro";
import site from "@/config/site";
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title={site.meta.title} description={site.meta.description}>
	<div class="animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-bottom-4 mx-auto max-w-2xl p-8 md:p-16">
		<Hero />

<section class="mt-16 space-y-5">
	<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">
		About Me
	</h2>

	<p class="text-base leading-7 text-muted-foreground">
		I’m James, a Data Analyst based in Reading, Berkshire. I enjoy using data,
		analysis and technology to solve problems, improve processes and make
		information easier to understand.
	</p>

	<p class="text-base leading-7 text-muted-foreground">
		I work with Python, SQL, PostgreSQL, Docker, Tableau and Power BI, with a
		focus on practical data analytics, automation and dashboard projects.
	</p>

	<p class="text-base leading-7 text-muted-foreground">
		This website is where I share my learning, projects and progress as I
		continue developing my skills in advanced analytics and Python development.
	</p>

	<p class="text-base leading-7 text-muted-foreground">
		Away from data, I’m into ice hockey, football, photography and cooking.
		I support the Anaheim Ducks, Reading FC and my best dish is a fantastic
		Mutton curry!
	</p>
</section>